DeliveryTypes.name: Designated Chest
DeliveryTypes.desc: When delivered, FlexCrop will find or place a chest for your items.

DeliveryTypes.name: Inventory
DeliveryTypes.desc: FlexCrop will place items in your inventory if there is space. This has a chance of removing all armour you are wearing at the time of delivery.

DeliveryTypes.name: Ender Chest
DeliveryTypes.desc: FlexCrop will place items in your ender chest if there is space. This has a chance of removing all armour you are wearing at the time of delivery.

DeliveryTypes.name: Safe
DeliveryTypes.desc: When delivered, FlexCrop will find or place a safe with you as the owner or the gift reciever for your items.

DeliveryTypes.name: Present
DeliveryTypes.desc: FlexCrop will place a Dalek Mod present with the items you ordered inside. Will not work with items that spawn others, like cars.

DeliveryTypes.name: Entity Only
DeliveryTypes.desc: This delivery type is for if you only have entities

SiteInfo.warning: It is discouraged to order from FlexCrop until 1.16. Once out, all 1.12 orders will be cancelled.
